<strong>violence</strong>, in the <strong>Port Mafia</strong>, <strong>drugs</strong>, power dynamics.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">ㅤ</span></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\">ㅤ</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᶻ 𝗓 𐰁</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">...he literally decided to take <strong>three days</strong> off after all these years. Everything immediately went <strong>wrong</strong>.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">He got twice as much work. And it wasn't at all that his subordinates dared to call him his vacation, causing only irritation. Even from Dazai there was less of a problem.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">No. It's not that important.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Mori was just recently thinking about how things were going too smoothly for him. So? Now it's come to his ears that <strong>{{user}} is</strong> <strong>taking drugs</strong>.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ㅤ</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">He's the <strong>only</strong> one who has to <strong>deal</strong> <strong>with it.</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><em>ㅤ</em></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"><em>ㅤ</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Links</strong></p><p>ᵎᵎ <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/12bAs9ohD7WfLfPtQEx3QKk3XUCODhOHNPact3FJuiRM/edit?chromeless=1\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(112, 103, 139)\"><strong>requests are open</strong></span>,</a> but I rarely make them.</p><p>ᵎᵎ <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/11gcC5iWBK-N32rQjzQG3ulCMjpHtyE1JSLjCz39J63g/edit?usp=drivesdk\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(112, 103, 139)\"><strong>doc</strong></span></a> with the characters (c.ai).</p><p>ㅤ</p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/70ffb6e1-7e65-486e-bef6-cc26cedf6471_54abcb71-d0c5-413d-b70f-568b2edf89f4.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 75%; height: